summary: These Two Are Way Too Alike
title: These Two Are Way Too Alike
body:
Deku from My Hero Academia, & Tohru from Fruits Basket.

The biggest flaw for both of these characters is that they put others before themselves to the point that it’s sometimes absurdly self-destructive…

This manifests in different ways between the two series since I’m comparing a character from a drama/romance/slice-of-life-ish anime with a character from an action anime lol.

They are both also complete spazzy softies when it comes to always having something nice to say about someone (Deku is ever the fanboy, and Tohru is… Tohru).  Then even more so, they both fail at keeping secrets yet all the while somehow managing to keep their biggest secret safe (by a hair).

Despite being from completely different genres the similarities between the two really jump out at me.  I hope they both learn that it’s ok to rely on others more. ;_;
